# Oxpecker API
-----------------------------
users/authentication                                  << head   << (<username|email:string>, password:string) << sign in
users/registration                                    << post   << (username:string, email:string, password:string)  << sign up
users/list                                            << get    << void << get users list
users/                                                << get    << void << get user details
users/                                                << put    << (details:json) << update user details
users/                                                << delete << void << disable user account
users/token                                           << post   << void << generate token for activation link
users/token                                           << get    << void << get current user token value
users/help                                            << get    << void << developer guide
-----------------------------
games/<gcode|name>                                    << head   << void << check game existence
games/<gcode|name>                                    << get    << void << get game details
games/search                                          << get    << (keyword:string) << fetch list of games which have this keyword
games/                                                << post   << (name:string, is_commercial:bool, license:string, details:json, attach:file) << add new game
games/<gcode>                                         << put    << (name:string, is_commercial:bool, license:string, details:json, attach:file) << update game
games/<gcode>                                         << delete << void << disable game
games/<gcode>/star                                    << put    << (user:string) << set star on game
games/<gcode>/bake                                    << post   << (user:string)  << serve game for user
games/<gcode>/notifies                                << get    << void  << get list of all emails which sent to users of game
games/<gcode>/notifies                                << post   << void  << send email to users of game
games/<gcode>/comments                                << get    << void << get comments of game
games/<gcode>/comments                                << post   << (user:string, title:string, body:string, is_private:bool) << add new comment
games/<gcode>/comments/<cid>/replay                   << post   << (user:string, title:string, body:string) << replay to comment
games/<gcode>/comments/<cid>report                    << post   << (user:string) << report comment
games/<gcode>/comments/<cid>/like                     << put    << (user:string) << like comment
games/<gcode>/comments/<cid>                          << delete << void << delete comment
games/help                                            << get    << void << developer guide
-----------------------------
